---
// AboutSection component - PetZo style
---

<section class="about-section" id="about">
  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-images">
      <div class="about-img"><img src="/images/puppies/maggie.jpg" alt="Cavalier King Charles Spaniel from Harris Heritage Cavaliers" loading="lazy"></div>
      <div class="about-img"><img src="/images/puppies/rose.jpg" alt="Cavalier puppy ready for a home" loading="lazy"></div>
      <div class="about-img"><img src="/images/puppies/emmy.jpg" alt="Adorable Cavalier puppy" loading="lazy"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-content">
      <span class="section-badge">About Us</span>
      <h2 class="about-title">About <span>Harris Heritage Cavaliers</span></h2>
      <p class="about-description">Welcome to Harris Heritage Cavaliers, where we specialize in raising healthy, happy, and well-socialized Cavalier King Charles Spaniel puppies. Our family has been dedicated to breeding exceptional companions with the utmost care and attention.</p>
      <p class="about-description">Each of our puppies is raised in a loving family environment, ensuring they are confident, well-adjusted, and ready to become the heart of your family. We are committed to the health, temperament, and beauty of every Cavalier we breed.</p>
      <div class="about-features">
        <div class="feature"><span class="feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg></span>Puppies Raised in Our Home</div>
        <div class="feature"><span class="feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg></span>Vet Checked & Vaccinated</div>
        <div class="feature"><span class="feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg></span>Health Guarantee Included</div>
        <div class="feature"><span class="feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg></span>Lifetime Breeder Support</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section { display: block; font-family: var(--font-family, 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif); background: #FFFFFF; padding: 5rem 1.5rem; }
  .about-container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: center; }
  .about-images { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
  .about-img { border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border: 3px solid transparent; transition: border-color 0.3s ease; }
  .about-img:hover { border-color: #F5C518; }
  .about-img:first-child { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
  .about-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
  .about-img:first-child img { height: 300px; }
  .about-img:not(:first-child) img { height: 220px; }
  .about-content { padding: 1rem 0; }
  .section-badge { display: inline-block; background: #F5C518; color: #1A1A1A; padding: 0.4rem 1rem; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .about-title { font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1A1A1A; margin: 0 0 1rem; line-height: 1.2; }
  .about-title span { color: #1A1A1A; position: relative; }
  .about-title span::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: 2px; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 6px; background: #F5C518; opacity: 0.4; z-index: -1; }
  .about-description { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #666; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; }
  .about-features { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .feature { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #333; font-weight: 500; }
  .feature-icon { width: 24px; height: 24px; background: #F5C518; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .feature-icon svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; fill: #1A1A1A; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .about-container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; } .about-images { order: -1; } .about-title { font-size: 1.75rem; } }
  @media (max-width: 600px) { .about-section { padding: 3rem 1rem; } .about-features { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .about-img:first-child img { height: 250px; } .about-img:not(:first-child) img { height: 180px; } }
</style>
